The paper deals with image and video processing, specifically semantic segmentation and background cut. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also mentions the use of a spatial-temporal refinement network, which falls under the category of multimedia (cs.MM). The paper also discusses the creation of a dataset, which could fall under the category of graphics (cs.GR). The paper also mentions the use of an end-to-end network, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
